{"tid":1183589,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉子千 隨母姓改名章立衡","createTime":"2019-06-03T04:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T04:51:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7c27fa0fe74df84bed16642c484202f9c439d7","tid":1183589,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"台灣名音樂人劉家昌跟前妻甄珍鬧爭產風波，劉家昌三度告甄珍，還公開大罵兒子劉子千是「畜生」，父子關係決裂多年，直至去年3月，兩父子突然開記者會宣告重修關係，劉家昌聲稱不再告甄珍。沒料，最終劉家昌指甄珍說謊，反口再告前妻。<br />\n<br />\n近日在演藝圈重新出發的劉子千突然在社交網顯示改名「章立衡」，不再跟爸爸姓，而改跟媽媽甄珍（原名章家珍）的姓氏。有報道指甄珍對兒子改名表示尊重。劉子千多年來跟爸爸關係麻麻，自小跟媽媽一家人長大，今次他突然改名，似是決心脫離爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BoVome5.eyFPe66Q.ZXROA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ3Ni45MDAxNDkwMzEyOTY1Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/0pp34wfgKh2rG.yq_tpCdQ--~B/aD0xMDAwO3c9MTM0MjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02d_enp01p12010619copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBoVome5.eyFPe66Q.ZXROA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ3Ni45MDAxNDkwMzEyOTY1Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0pp34wfgKh2rG.yq_tpCdQ--~B%2FaD0xMDAwO3c9MTM0MjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02d_enp01p12010619copy.jpg&h=674bde3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec4c8649785d909d57e0ece887a169c7980d1a31","tid":1183589,"uid":73547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"我的字典裡沒有...."},{"pid":"3904c78bba4e0c1ad9c8f35bd1044dc4db6d4e10","tid":1183589,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"一屋三姓"},{"pid":"53e8ee33d83679aa03332b91db95e2931db733ce","tid":1183589,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec4c8649785d909d57e0ece887a169c7980d1a31","tid":1183589,"uid":73547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"我的字典裡沒有...."},"c